WEBVTT

1
00:06:26.671 --> 00:06:33.026
This time we have the maximum
number of people who are getting

2
00:06:33.026 --> 00:06:42.777
married. Still I don't know
the final number.

3
00:06:42.777 --> 00:06:47.571
Even at the last moment some people
come to me that I should tie

4
00:06:47.571 --> 00:06:55.962
their dhotis. Different thing
in Sahaja Yoga doesn't matter.

5
00:06:57.044 --> 00:07:01.765
Whatever it is, there is one
thing I would first again ask.

6
00:07:01.765 --> 00:07:06.280
Those who don't want to get
married with the people whom

7
00:07:06.280 --> 00:07:10.925
we have selected and you accepted
should immediately tell me today.

8
00:07:10.925 --> 00:07:15.505
Now there's still time.
If you have any doubts, any one.

9
00:07:19.430 --> 00:07:22.430
Thank you very much.

10
00:07:26.725 --> 00:07:33.845
The purpose of these marriages
is this, that we should have

11
00:07:34.302 --> 00:07:42.501
international understanding about
human beings that after coming

12
00:07:42.501 --> 00:07:47.995
to Sahaja Yoga you transcend
all the barriers, all the barriers

13
00:07:47.995 --> 00:08:01.517
of race, religion [UNCLEAR], and nationality.
We have to create this homogenous

14
00:08:01.517 --> 00:08:12.080
world and make it peaceful by
removing this disease of national

15
00:08:13.545 --> 00:08:17.163
identification or racial
identification.

16
00:08:17.776 --> 00:08:24.924
We are all created by God Almighty.
Our differences are only skin deep.

17
00:08:25.226 --> 00:08:30.057
Culturally we are different
little bit here and there but

18
00:08:30.057 --> 00:08:35.450
basically in ourselves we are
all spiritual.

19
00:08:36.398 --> 00:08:42.984
And the religion that we have
is innate built in within us

20
00:08:42.984 --> 00:08:45.984
which is an part and parcel of us.

21
00:08:47.307 --> 00:08:54.707
By these marriages we want to
achieve a very happy and a very

22
00:08:54.707 --> 00:09:01.352
enjoyable married life.
In the marriage one has to know that,

23
00:09:01.994 --> 00:09:09.216
nobody should dominate anyone,
that's a wrong idea.

24
00:09:09.533 --> 00:09:14.442
But we have two wheels of the
chariot, one is big and one is

25
00:09:14.442 --> 00:09:18.714
small, then the chariot will
never move forward, it will go

26
00:09:18.714 --> 00:09:23.121
round and round.
Both are equally the same,

27
00:09:23.762 --> 00:09:27.478
equal sized, but they are
not similar.

28
00:09:28.016 --> 00:09:31.253
The left cannot be put to the right
and the right cannot be put

29
00:09:31.253 --> 00:09:35.974
to the left. So men and women
have to be men and women

30
00:09:35.974 --> 00:09:39.432
in Sahaja Yoga.
They cannot be unisex people.

31
00:09:39.432 --> 00:09:42.977
They cannot be.
That's very important.

32
00:09:42.977 --> 00:09:46.837
The man has to protect the wife,
love her, give her all the security

33
00:09:46.837 --> 00:09:51.045
that is needed. And woman has to
nourish the husband and give him

34
00:09:51.045 --> 00:09:54.415
all the love and affection she has.

35
00:09:56.191 --> 00:10:01.059
So here we are on the threshold
of entering into a new life

36
00:10:01.059 --> 00:10:06.546
where you have a companion
of your own. She will be your wife.

37
00:10:07.511 --> 00:10:13.112
Not because only she is in
Sahaja Yoga that you have married her

38
00:10:13.112 --> 00:10:17.068
but she's your own.
So try to prove it to her

39
00:10:17.068 --> 00:10:22.297
that you love her very much
and that she is your wife

40
00:10:22.297 --> 00:10:26.388
and you have all that is yours
is for her.

41
00:10:26.388 --> 00:10:31.118
This is very important
in the very beginning of it.

42
00:10:31.118 --> 00:10:34.585
Now there's another thing
I have found out in my experience

43
00:10:34.585 --> 00:10:38.184
sometimes that they get married,
I don't know what happens,

44
00:10:38.184 --> 00:10:40.303
they are swayed into it
and they get mad.

45
00:10:40.303 --> 00:10:43.398
And after they go back to
their own country they start saying

46
00:10:43.398 --> 00:10:48.456
"Mother we know we cannot manage,
we have to work it out. This, that"

47
00:10:48.456 --> 00:10:53.046
Marriages are now worked out.
Spontaneously it happens.

48
00:10:53.046 --> 00:10:57.710
But in India you see we are
all the time prepared for

49
00:10:57.710 --> 00:11:01.710
a good married life.
The wife is told, the husband

50
00:11:01.710 --> 00:11:05.944
is told all the time.
So normally when they get married

51
00:11:05.944 --> 00:11:09.295
they think that this is
what it is for us.

52
00:11:09.295 --> 00:11:12.186
They don't have love affairs
before hand; they don't have

53
00:11:12.186 --> 00:11:13.519
friends and things.

54
00:11:13.519 --> 00:11:17.538
But even if you had your past,
now it's finished.

55
00:11:17.538 --> 00:11:22.580
You don't discuss, don't tell,
don't talk about it to your brides.

56
00:11:22.580 --> 00:11:26.268
That's absolutely wrong because
the past doesn't exist,

57
00:11:26.268 --> 00:11:30.447
what exists is the present.
So enjoy the present,

58
00:11:30.447 --> 00:11:34.079
forget it, forgive yourself.
Many people also have this

59
00:11:34.079 --> 00:11:38.572
big problem that they cannot
forget their past and go on

60
00:11:38.572 --> 00:11:41.997
telling their wives
that I was like this.

61
00:11:41.997 --> 00:11:44.219
There is no need
to confess anything.

62
00:11:44.219 --> 00:11:47.054
They think it is honest.
There is no question of honesty

63
00:11:47.054 --> 00:11:56.091
or dishonesty at that time
is but to enjoy full joyous

64
00:11:56.091 --> 00:11:59.953
mood of marriage.
That's in the end.

65
00:11:59.953 --> 00:12:03.860
Otherwise what's the use of
marrying and then telling stories.

66
00:12:03.891 --> 00:12:07.352
Or some people have very
bad habit of telling him

67
00:12:07.352 --> 00:12:10.352
how bad the mother was,
the father was or may be

68
00:12:10.352 --> 00:12:13.620
that how miserable he is
or how he has gone through

69
00:12:13.620 --> 00:12:16.620
struggle… there's no need
to talk of this.

70
00:12:16.620 --> 00:12:20.123
At this moment you are married,
she is your wife,

71
00:12:20.123 --> 00:12:24.948
and you have to express
all your love and all your

72
00:12:24.948 --> 00:12:30.102
attention to her so she
feels secure and happy with you.

73
00:12:30.554 --> 00:12:36.197
This point please try to note.
Nothing has to be talked

74
00:12:36.197 --> 00:12:37.708
about your past.

75
00:12:40.327 --> 00:12:44.707
Then we are Sahaja Yogis.
I have seen some Sahaja Yogis,

76
00:12:44.707 --> 00:12:47.251
very great Sahaja Yogis
who are married,

77
00:12:47.251 --> 00:12:53.117
very very ordinary men,
very ordinary, ordinary

78
00:12:53.117 --> 00:12:56.441
looking superficially.
Or can say some of them

79
00:12:56.441 --> 00:13:00.269
could be called as ugly.
Some girls are like that,

80
00:13:00.269 --> 00:13:02.957
some men are like that.
I mean from these norms

81
00:13:02.957 --> 00:13:07.094
that you have about beauty
and all this nonsense.

82
00:13:07.565 --> 00:13:11.205
But when you see a person
full of vibrations,

83
00:13:11.205 --> 00:13:16.561
she gives you such tranquility,
such joy.


84
00:13:16.561 --> 00:13:21.481
Don't disturb it by having
your pre-married ideas

85
00:13:21.481 --> 00:13:27.290
about your wife you see.
The reality is this is your wife

86
00:13:27.290 --> 00:13:32.551
and you are her husband.
Take the reality into consideration.

87
00:13:32.551 --> 00:13:37.621
Not some imaginary image
you have about your wife.

88
00:13:38.331 --> 00:13:42.024
Your wife is before you,
she's your wife.

89
00:13:42.024 --> 00:13:47.061
What's the use of having
imaginary ideas but you will never

90
00:13:47.061 --> 00:13:50.407
enjoy your married life,
I mean if you have imagination,

91
00:13:50.407 --> 00:13:53.006
then you should not even marry:
marry your imagination

92
00:13:53.006 --> 00:13:57.139
is a better way.
Why to ruin somebody's life,

93
00:13:57.139 --> 00:14:01.119
why to make somebody miserable?
They are all intelligent

94
00:14:01.119 --> 00:14:04.019
and good Sahaja Yoginis.
We have seen to it

95
00:14:04.019 --> 00:14:07.069
they are all very good
Sahaja Yogis should be there.

96
00:14:07.069 --> 00:14:10.462
But once you try to misbehave
with your wife or try to

97
00:14:10.462 --> 00:14:14.031
create problems for us,
naturally we don't want you

98
00:14:14.031 --> 00:14:17.064
any more in Sahaja Yoga,
because it is getting too much

99
00:14:17.064 --> 00:14:22.238
and you know as it is not
easy to marry you,

100
00:14:22.238 --> 00:14:24.629
to get your visas,
to take you down there

101
00:14:24.629 --> 00:14:28.366
its quite a lot of work
one has to go into.

102
00:14:28.366 --> 00:14:31.824
So now don't think that
you have been forced into

103
00:14:31.824 --> 00:14:35.963
any marriage, you have been
asked into any marriage, please.

104
00:14:35.963 --> 00:14:44.148
If you give up this kind
of an imaginary ideas

105
00:14:44.148 --> 00:14:48.214
about this marriage,
again and again I am telling

106
00:14:48.214 --> 00:14:52.334
to you today now and
this time also, this present moment,

107
00:14:52.334 --> 00:14:55.508
all those who feel that way
should immediately tell me,

108
00:14:55.508 --> 00:14:57.944
I will be extremely happy.


109
00:15:00.794 --> 00:15:03.072
There is another third thing
that I have seen about

110
00:15:03.072 --> 00:15:05.589
the western people is that
they are literally frightened

111
00:15:05.589 --> 00:15:09.931
of marriage, literally frightened.

112
00:15:09.931 --> 00:15:16.608
First is they may live with
a woman for 10 days or 20 days

113
00:15:16.608 --> 00:15:21.198
or 10 years, but as soon as
they get married they go

114
00:15:21.198 --> 00:15:26.069
