For this I think the law

115
00:15:26.069 --> 00:15:30.117
is responsible, because the
women think they will get

116
00:15:30.117 --> 00:15:32.816
money out of their husbands
may be or the husbands think

117
00:15:32.816 --> 00:15:37.364
that they will get money
out of their wives.

118
00:15:43.184 --> 00:15:49.972
In Sahaja Yoga if you want
to take the divorce later on,

119
00:15:49.972 --> 00:15:55.148
which I don't like at all.
We have only 1% divorces,

120
00:15:55.148 --> 00:16:04.099
then I would not allow you
to extract money from the other part,

121
00:16:05.595 --> 00:16:12.067
never, and nor the girl
should extract money from you.

122
00:16:14.982 --> 00:16:19.728
Last but not the least is
important that, once you

123
00:16:19.728 --> 00:16:25.448
are married, now the girls
may not be able to go immediately

124
00:16:25.448 --> 00:16:29.953
from their various places
because of visa problem,

125
00:16:30.621 --> 00:16:37.522
but don't give them money
to be sent to their families,


126
00:16:37.522 --> 00:16:40.208
that is not allowed
in Sahaja Yoga.

127
00:16:41.406 --> 00:16:45.744
The girl should not send
their money to their parents

128
00:16:45.744 --> 00:16:49.273
that's not allowed and
trouble the husband for that.

129
00:16:50.917 --> 00:16:53.934
Sometimes if you want to
send is alright, but there

130
00:16:53.934 --> 00:16:56.230
should not be regular
remittance all the time

131
00:16:56.990 --> 00:17:02.748
and this is sometimes comes
to my notice which I do not

132
00:17:02.748 --> 00:17:06.831
want to encourage.
As far as that part is concerned

133
00:17:06.831 --> 00:17:13.488
you should not give any money
for sending it to the relations

134
00:17:13.488 --> 00:17:23.050
of your wife otherwise it
will become a money oriented

135
00:17:23.050 --> 00:17:28.478
marriage and people would marry
because they can extract

136
00:17:28.478 --> 00:17:29.925
some money from it.

137
00:17:34.455 --> 00:17:39.060
All these things should be
kept in to it, that we are

138
00:17:39.060 --> 00:17:43.552
now married in Sahaja Yoga,
we are stupid if we want

139
00:17:43.552 --> 00:17:49.620
to have a divorce, stupid.
And I don't like divorce at all.

140
00:17:49.620 --> 00:17:52.592
Though I allow because
sometimes I find horrible

141
00:17:52.592 --> 00:17:56.347
things happening.
But rarely I would allow

142
00:17:56.347 --> 00:18:01.280
anybody to have a divorce,
rarely, so this idea

143
00:18:01.280 --> 00:18:04.346
should be given up and
one should not be [UNCLEAR]

144
00:18:04.346 --> 00:18:07.943
But from the very beginning
if you try to be kind

145
00:18:07.943 --> 00:18:12.580
and nice, I am sure
things will work out.

146
00:18:12.580 --> 00:18:17.307
We have to prove to the world
that marriage is a divine

147
00:18:17.307 --> 00:18:23.258
institution and by this
divine institution if you

148
00:18:23.258 --> 00:18:28.631
have been put together
it's also a divine plan.

149
00:18:28.631 --> 00:18:33.022
And through this divine plan
many things are going to work out.

150
00:18:33.037 --> 00:18:36.704
So those who are getting married
today are helping

151
00:18:36.704 --> 00:18:39.369
Sahaja Yoga very much.
I have already told you

152
00:18:39.369 --> 00:18:41.955
there are many saints
who want to be married.

153
00:18:41.955 --> 00:18:45.234
And nowadays that you see
this world full of horrible people.

154
00:18:45.234 --> 00:18:49.367
We need so many saints to
be born and so the saints

155
00:18:49.367 --> 00:18:54.857
will be born in case you
have good married time,

156
00:18:54.857 --> 00:18:59.052
happy married life
and enjoyable life.

157
00:19:01.116 --> 00:19:05.997
I think all this lecturing
is of no use unless and until

158
00:19:05.997 --> 00:19:08.640
you start enjoying
your married life.

159
00:19:08.663 --> 00:19:11.803
There are such sweet things
I need not tell you.

160
00:19:11.803 --> 00:19:15.089
I was surprised that there
is no book in English language

161
00:19:15.089 --> 00:19:19.522
which describes the romance
after marriage, very surprised,

162
00:19:19.522 --> 00:19:22.868
no book, can you imagine?
And in India you won't find

163
00:19:22.868 --> 00:19:26.943
any books which describe
the romance before the marriage.

164
00:19:26.943 --> 00:19:29.667
Nowadays they have started
doing some sort of stupid things

165
00:19:29.667 --> 00:19:36.264
but normally no question.
So now it is for you,

166
00:19:36.264 --> 00:19:43.793
enjoy your married life
much more than you have enjoyed

167
00:19:43.793 --> 00:19:50.621
your childhood, your youth
or any other times in college,

168
00:19:50.621 --> 00:19:52.134
schools, anywhere.


169
00:19:53.291 --> 00:19:57.544
So be prepared. Make yourself
ready, you can do it,

170
00:19:57.544 --> 00:20:00.172
open your hearts.
Don't try to find faults

171
00:20:00.172 --> 00:20:02.738
in your wife. I mean some
things she doesn't know,

172
00:20:02.738 --> 00:20:05.303
some things you don't know.
Doesn't matter.

173
00:20:05.303 --> 00:20:09.173
All the time trying to
find faults makes you faulty.

174
00:20:09.173 --> 00:20:12.448
Don't find faults.
If you see somebody doing

175
00:20:12.448 --> 00:20:14.935
something wrong, suppose if
you find that person is

176
00:20:14.935 --> 00:20:19.707
trying to do something.
All right, you just do it

177
00:20:19.707 --> 00:20:23.991
your self or don't tell.
Gradually she will learn

178
00:20:23.991 --> 00:20:27.628
from you what is
the right way is.

179
00:20:27.628 --> 00:20:31.694
And one should make fun
of these moments, for example

180
00:20:31.694 --> 00:20:38.051
I don't know how to do
any banking, write a cheque.

181
00:20:38.051 --> 00:20:40.823
I am very bad at many
things you see, can't even

182
00:20:40.823 --> 00:20:45.585
open a television, I can't
even the air conditioner.

183
00:20:45.585 --> 00:20:49.311
So many things I just can't do.
Doesn't matter.

184
00:20:49.311 --> 00:20:53.657
My husband also equally the same.
So we enjoy each other.

185
00:20:53.657 --> 00:20:58.290
All part and parcel of Sahaja Yoga.
One unit here, one unit there,

186
00:20:58.290 --> 00:21:05.400
one unit there. But they are
in the same ocean of spirituality.

187
00:21:06.313 --> 00:21:12.234
So any Sahaja Yogi who comes
to your house or any one,

188
00:21:12.234 --> 00:21:14.927
especially Indian women
you will find, they will

189
00:21:14.927 --> 00:21:18.983
look after the guests very well.
And then there is some sort

190
00:21:18.983 --> 00:21:22.164
of a thing called jealousy
comes out which it's absurd.

191
00:21:22.164 --> 00:21:26.270
Indian women will not have
anybody else as their husbands

192
00:21:26.270 --> 00:21:29.005
but their own.
It is then worked out.

193
00:21:29.005 --> 00:21:33.472
So don't have these funny
ideas that she is very friendly,

194
00:21:33.472 --> 00:21:36.572
she is looking after other
people, this and that.

195
00:21:36.572 --> 00:21:39.137
This kind of a nonsense
should not be allowed.

196
00:21:39.137 --> 00:21:42.471
In Sahaja Yoga we don't have
those things, we have become

197
00:21:42.471 --> 00:21:47.201
very pure, their eyes are pure.
So don't have any doubts

198
00:21:47.201 --> 00:21:51.354
about your wives.
Same with the wives I will tell you.

199
00:21:51.354 --> 00:21:57.611
This will make your life
very much more happier and confident.

200
00:21:57.611 --> 00:22:02.279
If you have any problem
you can always write to me directly.

201
00:22:02.279 --> 00:22:05.633
Need not even go through
your leaders but you can

202
00:22:05.633 --> 00:22:09.968
directly write to me
if you really have problem.

203
00:22:09.968 --> 00:22:13.503
But I think you are all
intelligent people,

204
00:22:13.503 --> 00:22:16.503
you should be able to
sort out everything.   

205
00:30:10.503 --> 00:30:18.949
The tradition of India is that the girl
has to accept her husband.

206
00:30:19.952 --> 00:30:25.036
If she does not accept,
you cannot force marriage.

207
00:30:25.036 --> 00:30:27.433
That's why the first ceremony
we'll be having

208
00:30:27.433 --> 00:30:29.814
where they will be
garlanding you.

209
00:30:29.814 --> 00:30:33.526
By garlanding you, they suggest
they have accepted you.

210
00:30:34.747 --> 00:30:38.852
If a girl doesn't garland you,
when she has not accepted,

211
00:30:38.852 --> 00:30:42.546
then nobody in this whole world
can make them married.

212
00:30:42.546 --> 00:30:46.611
This freedom
we had from ancient times, I think.

213
00:30:46.611 --> 00:30:48.807
The systems in India
were very good.

214
00:30:48.807 --> 00:30:52.212
Now the people have become so funny
that I can't understand

215
00:30:52.212 --> 00:30:54.656
how they are doing
all these things.

216
00:30:54.656 --> 00:31:00.217
[UNCLEAR] everywhere,
but still in India,

217
00:31:00.217 --> 00:31:04.669
Their married lives are much better.
[UNCLEAR].

218
00:31:05.446 --> 00:31:08.321
So, thank you very much,
all of you.

219
00:31:10.996 --> 00:31:15.561
And please see
that you have your own bride before you

220
00:31:15.561 --> 00:31:20.979
when she garlands you.
Because there are so many.

221
00:31:20.979 --> 00:31:23.302
[UNCLEAR]

222
00:31:23.302 --> 00:31:26.210
Before, we never had done
this mistake.

223
00:31:26.210 --> 00:31:29.881
I think this time, again,
there won't be any mistake.

224
00:31:29.881 --> 00:31:39.709
Under the very experienced guidance
of Yogji,

225
00:31:39.709 --> 00:31:42.155
I'm sure it will work out.


226
00:31:44.255 --> 00:31:48.013
So, now I have to go
and prepare the brides

227
00:31:48.013 --> 00:31:50.287
for a very happy married life.

228
00:31:50.287 --> 00:31:53.287
May God bless you.

229
00:43:56.458 --> 00:44:04.054
Now I have been already
with your fiancés

230
00:44:04.054 --> 00:44:08.620
and I talked to them.
I have praised you a lot.

231
00:44:09.787 --> 00:44:15.869
Now first thing we have to know
that this marriage ceremony

232
00:44:16.346 --> 00:44:19.511
that we have organised
with a purpose.

233
00:44:21.218 --> 00:44:27.350
The first purpose is that regard marriage
is very essential for Sahaja Yoga.

234
00:44:28.124 --> 00:44:32.102
If somebody doesn’t want to marry,
we say alright you get out

235
00:44:32.102 --> 00:44:34.164
of Sahaja Yoga.
It’s alright.

236
00:44:34.439 --> 00:44:38.404
Now why marriage is important,
because the marriage

237
00:44:38.404 --> 00:44:47.586
is like a big Yagnya,
it’s like a big Tapasya,

238
00:44:47.586 --> 00:44:51.379
you can call it,
or it’s a great experience.

239
00:44:51.379 --> 00:44:55.956
How to achieve balance,
how to become a witness

240
00:44:55.956 --> 00:45:00.298
and how to become the Spirit.
It’s very important.

241
00:45:00.298 --> 00:45:06.224
Now the first and foremost thing
we have to know that

242
00:45:06.224 --> 00:45:11.813
he is your husband
and nobody else is your husband.

243
00:45:11.846 --> 00:45:14.813
Nobody is more important than he is.

244
00:45:14.813 --> 00:45:18.996
See men are very easy to be controlled.


245
00:45:18.996 --> 00:45:22.951
If you can make them feel
they are the most important people

246
00:45:22.951 --> 00:45:27.154
for you, then you can manage them
very well.

247
00:45:27.154 --> 00:45:34.178
But the first foremost ambition
should be or the idea should be

248
00:45:34.178 --> 00:45:37.761
that I will make my married life
extremely happy.

249
00:45:37.761 --> 00:45:41.098
Because if the married life is happy
you will be happy.

250
00:45:41.098 --> 00:45:43.485
Now men have a habit of sometimes
losing temper.

251
00:45:43.485 --> 00:45:46.231
Doesn’t matter that’s their habit.

252
00:45:46.231 --> 00:45:50.654
So you shouldn’t immediately
become the same type.

253
00:45:50.654 --> 00:45:54.682
But you can little bit
in a womanly way

254
00:45:54.682 --> 00:46:06.844
try to put your sweet device
of smiling it or laughing it out

255
00:46:06.844 --> 00:46:09.718
or little bit showing you are nice
somehow.

256
00:46:09.718 --> 00:46:13.216
But not to make it serious.
It’s very important.

257
00:46:13.216 --> 00:46:19.108
So how to handle the men.
Especially your husbands is an art

258
00:46:19.108 --> 00:46:22.874
and that art you will achieve
gradually when you start seeing.

259
00:46:22.874 --> 00:46:27.398
But if you start finding faults
with the men and start saying

260
00:46:27.398 --> 00:46:29.992
you can’t do this, you can’t do this,

261
00:46:29.992 --> 00:46:34.950
you don’t know how to drive
or how to do this, or these things.

262
00:46:34.950 --> 00:46:39.478
Then you are finished.
You must say you are the best driver.

263
00:46:39.478 --> 00:46:43.962
You are the best.
That’s the way you have to deal with them.

264
00:46:43.962 --> 00:46:45.927
But not that you are befooling them.


265
00:46:45.927 --> 00:46:48.927
Because you say this because you love them.


266
00:46:48.927 --> 00:46:51.198
And love is the basis
between you and him.

267
00:46:51.198 --> 00:46:53.640
Nothing else. Not Money.

268
00:46:53.640 --> 00:46:56.423
Not what you have got for him
or he has brought for you.

269
00:46:56.423 --> 00:46:57.593
Nothing of that kind.

270
00:46:57.593 --> 00:47:00.593
All these things are not materialistic.


271
00:47:00.593 --> 00:47:02.643
They have nothing to do with matter.


272
00:47:02.643 --> 00:47:08.373
Love is something which you can
express also through matter,

273
00:47:08.373 --> 00:47:13.437
sometimes by giving some nice presents
or nice food or something.

274
00:47:13.437 --> 00:47:15.906
But the most important thing
is your heart.

275
00:47:15.906 --> 00:47:20.471
You should not cheat.
In anyway you should not be hypocritical,

276
00:47:20.471 --> 00:47:27.510
and you should not try to do something
that is not pure.

277
00:47:27.510 --> 00:47:30.510
So in Sahaja Yoga,
the purpose of these marriages

278
00:47:30.510 --> 00:47:33.940
is to have you connected internationally.

279
00:47:33.940 --> 00:47:38.549
So you all transcend all the barriers
of your nationality,

280
00:47:38.549 --> 00:47:41.978
the barriers of our racialism,
barriers of caste,

281
00:47:41.978 --> 00:47:47.819
barriers of so much of materialism.

282
00:47:47.819 --> 00:47:51.055
So you should not compare
your husband with anyone.

283
00:47:51.055 --> 00:47:54.376
He is your husband
and you shouldn’t expect too much

284
00:47:54.376 --> 00:47:55.298
from him.

285
00:47:55.298 --> 00:47:57.685
He’s not given me this,
he has not done that for me,

286
00:47:57.685 --> 00:48:00.685
he’s like this.
This is not necessary.

287
00:48:00.685 --> 00:48:04.406
You must always think
what I have done for him.

288
00:48:04.406 --> 00:48:07.406
Also what’s wrong with me?


289
00:48:07.406 --> 00:48:12.390
Now some people,
especially in the west it’s very common,

290
00:48:12.390 --> 00:48:15.727
that after marriage they think
that they have to work out marriage,

291
00:48:15.727 --> 00:48:17.525
no working out.

292
00:48:17.531 --> 00:48:23.319
You see like they think that as you work
out your kitchen or work out your things.

293
00:48:23.319 --> 00:48:24.298
It’s not like that.

294
00:48:24.298 --> 00:48:29.616
It is spontaneously between the two
human beings who are realised souls.

295
00:48:29.838 --> 00:48:32.518
It is not that you are working out
anything,

296
00:48:32.518 --> 00:48:37.565
but spontaneously you are going to enjoy,
spontaneously.

297
00:48:37.565 --> 00:48:43.873
Now if you become extremely critical
and try to show you are very brilliant

298
00:48:43.873 --> 00:48:45.750
and this. It’s not going to work.


299
00:48:45.750 --> 00:48:48.965
To be humble. Keep quiet.


300
00:48:48.965 --> 00:48:52.865
Those who are really intelligent
always keep quiet and watch things.

301
00:48:52.865 --> 00:48:55.865
But those who are not, are bumptious.


302
00:48:57.427 --> 00:49:02.039
The more you are in Sahaja Yoga,
the more you will be respected by him

303
00:49:02.039 --> 00:49:04.540
and by everybody else.

304
00:49:04.540 --> 00:49:08.380
Apart from that, there are so many saints
who want to be born.

305
00:49:08.380 --> 00:49:12.742
Once you have very happy married life
among yourselves,

306
00:49:12.742 --> 00:49:14.839
those saints will be born to you,


307
00:49:14.839 --> 00:49:17.839
and it will be such a blessing
and joy for you.

308
00:49:17.839 --> 00:49:20.839
So try to understand
not to boss your husband

309
00:49:20.839 --> 00:49:26.637
or try to put him right or do things
and in a very.

310
00:49:26.637 --> 00:49:32.023
I have seen some ladies
who are extremely tense, very tense type.
 

311
00:49:32.023 --> 00:49:33.748
They can never give joy.


312
00:49:33.748 --> 00:49:36.974
They are themselves not in joy,
how can they give joy,

313
00:49:36.974 --> 00:49:41.530
So the tension should not be there.
At all of any kind. Be relaxed.

314
00:49:41.530 --> 00:49:43.485
You are the other side of Sahaja Yoga,


315
00:49:43.485 --> 00:49:50.731
which gives peace, joy, nourishment
and also complete tranquillity.

316
00:49:51.263 --> 00:49:55.239
In the family you are responsible
for tranquillity.

317
00:49:55.239 --> 00:49:57.845
Even if husband is angry,
children are fighting,

318
00:49:57.845 --> 00:50:01.957
if the mother is tranquil,
you can control all the situation.

319
00:50:01.957 --> 00:50:06.739
So the situation has to be controlled
in a way that you make life happy

320
00:50:06.739 --> 00:50:08.172
for everyone.

321
00:50:08.172 --> 00:50:14.705
Sometimes women feel very angry
when I tell them that first feed

322
00:50:14.705 --> 00:50:18.356
your children, your husband
and then you eat yourself.

323
00:50:18.356 --> 00:50:21.065
Because that is the job of a woman.


324
00:50:21.065 --> 00:50:26.033
Like a man should go, earn living,
do what he wants to do, job and all that.

325
00:50:26.033 --> 00:50:32.256
But the woman has to really look after
the husband, look after the family,

326
00:50:32.256 --> 00:50:34.014
look after everything.

327
00:50:34.014 --> 00:50:37.014
Also you will find our Indian husbands
not so good,

328
00:50:37.014 --> 00:50:39.408
as far as gardening is concerned,


329
00:50:39.408 --> 00:50:47.102
or you can say, they don’t know how
to mend anything like cars

330
00:50:47.102 --> 00:50:50.102
or your plumbing, they don’t know.

331
00:50:50.102 --> 00:50:51.848
So doesn’t matter, take it easy.

332
00:50:51.848 --> 00:50:55.961
Gradually they’ll become
and they’ll learn and they’ll do it.

333
00:50:55.961 --> 00:50:57.487
But don’t become impatient with them.

334
00:50:57.487 --> 00:51:00.401
Just make fun of it, you see,
just make fun.

335
00:51:00.401 --> 00:51:05.179
That the best way to manage it
and that don’t expect too much,

336
00:51:05.179 --> 00:51:06.681
that they will do this nicely.

337
00:51:06.681 --> 00:51:12.448
Sometimes they cannot clean the utensils
properly, they don’t know how to do it.

338
00:51:12.448 --> 00:51:16.055
So all right.
Just make fun of it and just enjoy it

339
00:51:16.055 --> 00:51:17.386
because they have no...

340
00:51:17.386 --> 00:51:20.398
You see in England or America
I have seen anywhere,

341
00:51:20.398 --> 00:51:22.334
they have no servants at all.

342
00:51:22.334 --> 00:51:25.744
While we have servants here
so all these boys are spoiled

343
00:51:25.744 --> 00:51:27.142
by the servants.

344
00:51:27.142 --> 00:51:31.841
So they are absolutely good for nothing
as far as these things are concerned.

345
00:51:31.841 --> 00:51:35.513
But if you just try to teach them
and help them,

346
00:51:35.513 --> 00:51:38.513
they will definitely go all out to do it.

347
00:51:38.513 --> 00:51:44.441
So the only thing you have to do
is to love them with a clear heart.

348
00:51:44.441 --> 00:51:47.441
And all the time forgive
and let them know

349
00:51:47.441 --> 00:51:51.044
that that she is the only one I have
in the whole world

350
00:51:51.044 --> 00:51:54.044
apart from the Holy Mother.

351
00:51:56.565 --> 00:52:00.990
Of course, I’m not against divorce,
but I’m not for it.

352
00:52:00.990 --> 00:52:03.990
In the sense that I don’t like people
when they divorce.

353
00:52:03.990 --> 00:52:06.295
But when things are impossible
and difficult

354
00:52:06.295 --> 00:52:10.773
and one has to go in for such a thing,
doesn’t matter.


355
00:52:10.773 --> 00:52:13.901
Sometimes one has to do it.
But it should be very rare.

356
00:52:13.901 --> 00:52:17.095
One should not think of a divorce at all.

357
00:52:17.095 --> 00:52:20.772
People think of divorce in the west
mostly because of the laws,

358
00:52:20.772 --> 00:52:23.772
because the wife gets the money
or the husband gets the money.

359
00:52:23.772 --> 00:52:28.021
But in SahajaYoga if you are marrying,
all these things even if you are divorced,

360
00:52:28.021 --> 00:52:29.739
I will not support.

361
00:52:29.739 --> 00:52:35.537
Moreover, another thing is that the wives
should not take money from the husband

362
00:52:35.537 --> 00:52:39.174
and send it to her relations. Never.


363
00:52:39.174 --> 00:52:44.522
It’s a very very wrong thing,
is to support your family

364
00:52:44.522 --> 00:52:47.103
through the money of their husband.

365
00:52:47.103 --> 00:52:50.651
Absolutely not allowed.
That should not be done.

366
00:52:50.651 --> 00:52:56.236
You should not put the pressure
of your family on your husband.

367
00:52:56.236 --> 00:53:01.257
You see there has to be a clear cut
understanding for all of you.

368
00:53:01.257 --> 00:53:07.847
That you will not take.
You must keep your self respect.

369
00:53:07.847 --> 00:53:09.793
Don’t ask for anything.

370
00:53:09.793 --> 00:53:11.825
If he gives you anything
well and good.

371
00:53:11.825 --> 00:53:16.619
But don’t ask, don’t demand.
That means you are not a Sahaja Yogi.

372
00:53:16.619 --> 00:53:20.275
If you are a satisfied soul
why should you ask for anything?

373
00:53:20.275 --> 00:53:23.322
Or somebody gets something,
she has got this, she has …

374
00:53:23.322 --> 00:53:25.902
Nothing of that kind.
You be satisfied people.

375
00:53:25.902 --> 00:53:31.388
and this is how some girls nag
the husbands very much.

376
00:53:31.388 --> 00:53:36.161
Most important thing is that
you should not talk about your past,

377
00:53:36.161 --> 00:53:38.368
at all. Because past is finished.

378
00:53:38.368 --> 00:53:42.429
Now you are Sahaja Yogis.
You are all realised souls.

379
00:53:42.429 --> 00:53:44.942
So you don’t have to say a word
about your past.

380
00:53:44.942 --> 00:53:48.313
Even if husband starts talking
you just stop,

381
00:53:48.313 --> 00:53:51.983
and tell him
we are to live in the present.

382
00:53:51.983 --> 00:53:54.226
Don’t tell us about your past.

383
00:53:54.226 --> 00:53:57.716
I don’t know why people think that
they will look more attractive

384
00:53:57.716 --> 00:54:00.716
if they talk about all the past
nonsense they did.

385
00:54:00.716 --> 00:54:04.811
Or say that my mother was so bad.
All psychological nonsense.

386
00:54:06.375 --> 00:54:10.926
Not to put your parents into jeopardy
by saying that they are very bad,

387
00:54:10.926 --> 00:54:13.365
they are no good. This, that..

388
00:54:13.365 --> 00:54:18.532
Just forget the past
and live in the present

389
00:54:18.532 --> 00:54:22.569
because in the present resides the reality

390
00:54:22.569 --> 00:54:26.021
and the reality is the ocean of joy.

391
00:54:27.423 --> 00:54:30.365
You should not nag him for anything.

392
00:54:30.365 --> 00:54:33.873
Supposing he does not like some things,
you shouldn’t do it.

393
00:54:33.873 --> 00:54:36.574
Whatever he doesn’t like, small things,
you know like,

394
00:54:36.574 --> 00:54:40.487
I was married in a family
which was culturally very different,

395
00:54:40.487 --> 00:54:44.113
very different.
And they don’t wear flowers.

396
00:54:44.113 --> 00:54:47.113
You see, and in India
all the married ladies,

397
00:54:47.113 --> 00:54:49.945
I mean down south,
I’m saying in my community,

398
00:54:49.945 --> 00:54:57.496
all wear garlands around their buns
and things is always there.

399
00:54:57.496 --> 00:55:00.417
My husband said no better not do it.

400
00:55:00.417 --> 00:55:05.355
Because you know here in our community
only the bad women wear that

401
00:55:05.355 --> 00:55:06.848
to attract people.

402
00:55:06.848 --> 00:55:08.827
Since that day I have never worn it.

403
00:55:08.827 --> 00:55:11.827
Doesn’t matter, not important.

404
00:55:11.827 --> 00:55:17.612
So, also you must understand
now you have to take to the style of life

405
00:55:17.612 --> 00:55:18.972
of your husband.

406
00:55:18.972 --> 00:55:22.605
He is fond of entertaining,
look after that.

407
00:55:22.605 --> 00:55:25.469
Women should be entertaining,
they should look after.

408
00:55:25.469 --> 00:55:28.068
They should not mind if somebody
comes to stay with them

409
00:55:28.068 --> 00:55:28.891
or lives with them.

410
00:55:28.891 --> 00:55:31.011
They should not try to show.


411
00:55:31.011 --> 00:55:34.500
On the contrary they should be happy
they are able to look after

412
00:55:34.500 --> 00:55:36.189
someone who is a Sahaja Yogi.

413
00:55:36.189 --> 00:55:40.138
So, for the Sahaja Yogis, you must
keep always your heart open,

414
00:55:40.138 --> 00:55:42.149
your house open.

415
00:55:43.268 --> 00:55:45.667
There are so many things
which I would like to tell you

416
00:55:45.667 --> 00:55:47.598
but in this short time,
I have to just say

417
00:55:47.598 --> 00:55:52.682
that it is the responsibility
of the women to make their

418
00:55:52.682 --> 00:55:55.067
marriages happy.

419
00:55:55.676 --> 00:56:01.507
Depends on their intelligence
and on their dedication

420
00:56:01.507 --> 00:56:04.507
to Sahaja Yoga.

421
00:56:04.507 --> 00:56:07.220
It's your responsibility.

422
00:56:07.220 --> 00:56:11.581
And if you see in a wider sense
the responsibility of making

423
00:56:11.581 --> 00:56:15.462
a good society is that of a woman.

424
00:56:15.462 --> 00:56:17.490
Even if she has to suffer she can.

425
00:56:17.490 --> 00:56:19.087
She is like this mother Earth.

426
00:56:19.087 --> 00:56:20.471
She can suffer anything.


427
00:56:20.471 --> 00:56:21.802
She never feels she suffers.

428
00:56:21.802 --> 00:56:23.038
She is so great.


429
00:56:23.038 --> 00:56:24.603
You are Shaktis.

430
00:56:24.603 --> 00:56:28.464
So as Shaktis if you have to suffer,
you don't mind.

431
00:56:28.464 --> 00:56:32.713
And what you have to feel
is that we are responsible

432
00:56:32.713 --> 00:56:37.878
for making our Sahaja Yoga
society a perfect society.

433
00:56:40.303 --> 00:56:42.370
That's our responsibility.

434
00:56:43.537 --> 00:56:47.991
All your greed, all your
ambitions, everything should

435
00:56:47.991 --> 00:56:53.653
be directed towards making
a very very happy married life.

436
00:56:55.062 --> 00:57:01.786
I wish, I wish all, all of you,
a very happy and prosperous

437
00:57:01.786 --> 00:57:03.760
married life.
